{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":325,"text":"In the middle of my Ph.D.,"},{"time":2388,"text":"I was hopelessly stuck."},{"time":5850,"text":"Every research direction that I tried"},{"time":7630,"text":"led to a dead end."},{"time":9246,"text":"It seemed like my basic assumptions"},{"time":11148,"text":"just stopped working."},{"time":13076,"text":"I felt like a pilot flying through the mist,"},{"time":16075,"text":"and I lost all sense of direction."},{"time":18870,"text":"I stopped shaving."},{"time":20351,"text":"I couldn't get out of bed in the morning."},{"time":23092,"text":"I felt unworthy"},{"time":24825,"text":"of stepping across the gates of the university,"},{"time":27978,"text":"because I wasn't like Einstein or Newton"},{"time":30126,"text":"or any other scientist whose results"},{"time":32279,"text":"I had learned about, because in science,"},{"time":33810,"text":"we just learn about the results, not the process."},{"time":37192,"text":"And so obviously, I couldn't be a scientist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41893,"text":"But I had enough support"},{"time":43557,"text":"and I made it through"},{"time":44954,"text":"and discovered something new about nature."},{"time":47174,"text":"This is an amazing feeling of calmness,"},{"time":49917,"text":"being the only person in the world"},{"time":51249,"text":"who knows a new law of nature."},{"time":53474,"text":"And I started the second project in my Ph.D,"},{"time":56516,"text":"and it happened again."},{"time":57880,"text":"I got stuck and I made it through."},{"time":60169,"text":"And I started thinking,"},{"time":61555,"text":"maybe there's a pattern here."},{"time":62712,"text":"I asked the other graduate students, and they said,"},{"time":64553,"text":"\"Yeah, that's exactly what happened to us,"},{"time":66596,"text":"except nobody told us about it.\""},{"time":68945,"text":"We'd all studied science as if it's a series"},{"time":70895,"text":"of logical steps between question and answer,"},{"time":74471,"text":"but doing research is nothing like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77217,"text":"At the same time, I was also studying"},{"time":79551,"text":"to be an improvisation theater actor."},{"time":81638,"text":"So physics by day,"},{"time":83072,"text":"and by night, laughing, jumping, singing,"},{"time":85090,"text":"playing my guitar."},{"time":86402,"text":"Improvisation theater,"},{"time":87881,"text":"just like science, goes into the unknown,"},{"time":90890,"text":"because you have to make a scene onstage"},{"time":92302,"text":"without a director, without a script,"},{"time":94005,"text":"without having any idea what you'll portray"},{"time":96283,"text":"or what the other characters will do."},{"time":98689,"text":"But unlike science,"},{"time":100538,"text":"in improvisation theater, they tell you from day one"},{"time":103561,"text":"what's going to happen to\nyou when you get onstage."},{"time":105776,"text":"You're going to fail miserably."},{"time":108548,"text":"You're going to get stuck."},{"time":109725,"text":"And we would practice staying creative"},{"time":111843,"text":"inside that stuck place."},{"time":113046,"text":"For example, we had an exercise"},{"time":114951,"text":"where we all stood in a circle,"},{"time":116093,"text":"and each person had to do\nthe world's worst tap dance,"},{"time":119058,"text":"and everybody else applauded"},{"time":120644,"text":"and cheered you on,"},{"time":121886,"text":"supporting you onstage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124649,"text":"When I became a professor"},{"time":126557,"text":"and had to guide my own students"},{"time":127938,"text":"through their research projects,"},{"time":129911,"text":"I realized again,"},{"time":131278,"text":"I don't know what to do."},{"time":132990,"text":"I'd studied thousands of hours of physics,"},{"time":134984,"text":"biology, chemistry,"},{"time":136598,"text":"but not one hour, not one concept"},{"time":138970,"text":"on how to mentor, how to guide someone"},{"time":141556,"text":"to go together into the unknown,"},{"time":143293,"text":"about motivation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145214,"text":"So I turned to improvisation theater,"},{"time":147144,"text":"and I told my students from day one"},{"time":149317,"text":"what's going to happen when you start research,"},{"time":152218,"text":"and this has to do with our mental schema"},{"time":153944,"text":"of what research will be like."},{"time":155956,"text":"Because you see, whenever people do anything,"},{"time":158234,"text":"for example if I want to touch this blackboard,"},{"time":160876,"text":"my brain first builds up a schema,"},{"time":162536,"text":"a prediction of exactly what my muscles will do"},{"time":164395,"text":"before I even start moving my hand,"},{"time":166551,"text":"and if I get blocked,"},{"time":168399,"text":"if my schema doesn't match reality,"},{"time":170274,"text":"that causes extra stress called cognitive dissonance."},{"time":172558,"text":"That's why your schemas had better match reality."},{"time":175467,"text":"But if you believe the way science is taught,"},{"time":178622,"text":"and if you believe textbooks, you're liable"},{"time":180519,"text":"to have the following schema of research."},{"time":186813,"text":"If A is the question,"},{"time":190131,"text":"and B is the answer,"},{"time":193531,"text":"then research is a direct path."},{"time":198127,"text":"The problem is that if an experiment doesn't work,"},{"time":201242,"text":"or a student gets depressed,"},{"time":204904,"text":"it's perceived as something utterly wrong"},{"time":206990,"text":"and causes tremendous stress."},{"time":210020,"text":"And that's why I teach my students"},{"time":211803,"text":"a more realistic schema."},{"time":218860,"text":"Here's an example"},{"time":220384,"text":"where things don't match your schema."},{"time":226379,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":229641,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241564,"text":"So I teach my students a different schema."},{"time":245010,"text":"If A is the question,"},{"time":247204,"text":"B is the answer,"},{"time":253320,"text":"stay creative in the cloud,"},{"time":254855,"text":"and you start going,"},{"time":256830,"text":"and experiments don't work, experiments don't work,"},{"time":259193,"text":"experiments don't work, experiments don't work,"},{"time":261728,"text":"until you reach a place linked\nwith negative emotions"},{"time":264404,"text":"where it seems like your basic assumptions"},{"time":266682,"text":"have stopped making sense,"},{"time":267798,"text":"like somebody yanked the carpet beneath your feet."},{"time":270853,"text":"And I call this place the cloud."},{"time":287685,"text":"Now you can be lost in the cloud"},{"time":290363,"text":"for a day, a week, a month, a year,"},{"time":292871,"text":"a whole career,"},{"time":294369,"text":"but sometimes, if you're lucky enough"},{"time":296531,"text":"and you have enough support,"},{"time":298387,"text":"you can see in the materials at hand,"},{"time":300377,"text":"or perhaps meditating on the shape of the cloud,"},{"time":303625,"text":"a new answer,"},{"time":307285,"text":"C, and you decide to go for it."},{"time":310969,"text":"And experiments don't work, experiments don't work,"},{"time":313338,"text":"but you get there,"},{"time":314807,"text":"and then you tell everyone about it"},{"time":316027,"text":"by publishing a paper that reads A arrow C,"},{"time":319529,"text":"which is a great way to communicate,"},{"time":321488,"text":"but as long as you don't forget the path"},{"time":323832,"text":"that brought you there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325631,"text":"Now this cloud is an inherent part"},{"time":327606,"text":"of research, an inherent part of our craft,"},{"time":330210,"text":"because the cloud stands guard at the boundary."},{"time":337721,"text":"It stands guard at the boundary"},{"time":339990,"text":"between the known"},{"time":345795,"text":"and the unknown,"},{"time":353110,"text":"because in order to discover something truly new,"},{"time":355385,"text":"at least one of your basic\nassumptions has to change,"},{"time":358962,"text":"and that means that in science,"},{"time":360216,"text":"we do something quite heroic."},{"time":362178,"text":"Every day, we try to bring ourselves"},{"time":363999,"text":"to the boundary between\nthe known and the unknown"},{"time":365811,"text":"and face the cloud."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367632,"text":"Now notice that I put B"},{"time":369337,"text":"in the land of the known,"},{"time":370080,"text":"because we knew about it in the beginning,"},{"time":371891,"text":"but C is always more interesting"},{"time":375540,"text":"and more important than B."},{"time":378263,"text":"So B is essential in order to get going,"},{"time":380456,"text":"but C is much more profound,"},{"time":382274,"text":"and that's the amazing thing about resesarch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386771,"text":"Now just knowing that word, the cloud,"},{"time":388959,"text":"has been transformational in my research group,"},{"time":391514,"text":"because students come to me and say,"},{"time":393384,"text":"\"Uri, I'm in the cloud,\""},{"time":394982,"text":"and I say, \"Great, you must be feeling miserable.\""},{"time":398148,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":400290,"text":"But I'm kind of happy,"},{"time":402203,"text":"because we might be close to the boundary"},{"time":403881,"text":"between the known and the unknown,"},{"time":405777,"text":"and we stand a chance of discovering"},{"time":407323,"text":"something truly new,"},{"time":409184,"text":"since the way our mind works,"},{"time":410526,"text":"it's just knowing that the cloud"},{"time":413674,"text":"is normal, it's essential,"},{"time":418100,"text":"and in fact beautiful,"},{"time":419305,"text":"we can join the Cloud Appreciation Society,"},{"time":422928,"text":"and it detoxifies the feeling that something"},{"time":424846,"text":"is deeply wrong with me."},{"time":427408,"text":"And as a mentor, I know what to do,"},{"time":429858,"text":"which is to step up my support for the student,"},{"time":432060,"text":"because research in psychology shows"},{"time":433541,"text":"that if you're feeling fear and despair,"},{"time":437100,"text":"your mind narrows down"},{"time":438097,"text":"to very safe and conservative ways of thinking."},{"time":440928,"text":"If you'd like to explore the risky paths"},{"time":442503,"text":"needed to get out of the cloud,"},{"time":443891,"text":"you need other emotions --"},{"time":445652,"text":"solidarity, support, hope —"},{"time":447853,"text":"that come with your connection from somebody else,"},{"time":449590,"text":"so like in improvisation theater,"},{"time":451140,"text":"in science, it's best to walk into the unknown"},{"time":453441,"text":"together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455410,"text":"So knowing about the cloud,"},{"time":457852,"text":"you also learn from improvisation theater"},{"time":461176,"text":"a very effective way to have conversations"},{"time":463778,"text":"inside the cloud."},{"time":465538,"text":"It's based on the central principle"},{"time":467515,"text":"of improvisation theater,"},{"time":469282,"text":"so here improvisation theater"},{"time":470375,"text":"came to my help again."},{"time":471671,"text":"It's called saying \"Yes, and\""},{"time":473962,"text":"to the offers made by other actors."},{"time":484297,"text":"That means accepting the offers"},{"time":487191,"text":"and building on them, saying, \"Yes, and.\""},{"time":489702,"text":"For example, if one actor says,"},{"time":490941,"text":"\"Here is a pool of water,\""},{"time":492096,"text":"and the other actor says,"},{"time":493141,"text":"\"No, that's just a stage,\""},{"time":495010,"text":"the improvisation is over."},{"time":496748,"text":"It's dead, and everybody feels frustrated."},{"time":500520,"text":"That's called blocking."},{"time":501868,"text":"If you're not mindful of communications,"},{"time":503475,"text":"scientific conversations can have a lot of blocking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506412,"text":"Saying \"Yes, and\" sounds like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508648,"text":"\"Here is a pool of water.\"\n\"Yeah, let's jump in.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":511156,"text":"\"Look, there's a whale! Let's grab it by its tail."},{"time":514165,"text":"It's pulling us to the moon!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":516266,"text":"So saying \"Yes, and\" bypasses our inner critic."},{"time":519286,"text":"We all have an inner critic"},{"time":520980,"text":"that kind of guards what we say,"},{"time":522221,"text":"so people don't think that we're obscene"},{"time":524144,"text":"or crazy or unoriginal,"},{"time":525259,"text":"and science is full of the fear"},{"time":526519,"text":"of appearing unoriginal."},{"time":528076,"text":"Saying \"Yes, and\" bypasses the critic"},{"time":530243,"text":"and unlocks hidden voices of creativity"},{"time":532855,"text":"you didn't even know that you had,"},{"time":534380,"text":"and they often carry the answer"},{"time":536410,"text":"about the cloud."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538815,"text":"So you see, knowing about the cloud"},{"time":541416,"text":"and about saying \"Yes, and\""},{"time":542820,"text":"made my lab very creative."},{"time":545679,"text":"Students started playing off of each others' ideas,"},{"time":548207,"text":"and we made surprising discoveries"},{"time":550321,"text":"in the interface between physics and biology."},{"time":553190,"text":"For example, we were stuck for a year"},{"time":556140,"text":"trying to understand the intricate"},{"time":557289,"text":"biochemical networks inside our cells,"},{"time":559982,"text":"and we said, \"We are deeply in the cloud,\""},{"time":562439,"text":"and we had a playful conversation"},{"time":564419,"text":"where my student Shai Shen Orr said,"},{"time":566207,"text":"\"Let's just draw this on a\npiece of paper, this network,\""},{"time":569050,"text":"and instead of saying,"},{"time":570503,"text":"\"But we've done that so many times"},{"time":572654,"text":"and it doesn't work,\""},{"time":573688,"text":"I said, \"Yes, and"},{"time":576631,"text":"let's use a very big piece of paper,\""},{"time":578672,"text":"and then Ron Milo said,"},{"time":579764,"text":"\"Let's use a gigantic architect's"},{"time":581984,"text":"blueprint kind of paper, and I know where to print it,\""},{"time":583780,"text":"and we printed out the network and looked at it,"},{"time":586280,"text":"and that's where we made\nour most important discovery,"},{"time":588789,"text":"that this complicated network is just made"},{"time":590990,"text":"of a handful of simple, repeating interaction patterns"},{"time":594453,"text":"like motifs in a stained glass window."},{"time":597616,"text":"We call them network motifs,"},{"time":599664,"text":"and they're the elementary circuits"},{"time":601816,"text":"that help us understand"},{"time":603201,"text":"the logic of the way cells make decisions"},{"time":605901,"text":"in all organisms, including our body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608750,"text":"Soon enough, after this,"},{"time":610675,"text":"I started being invited to give talks"},{"time":612295,"text":"to thousands of scientists across the world,"},{"time":615306,"text":"but the knowledge about the cloud"},{"time":617139,"text":"and saying \"Yes, and\""},{"time":618271,"text":"just stayed within my own lab,"},{"time":620110,"text":"because you see, in science,\nwe don't talk about the process,"},{"time":622241,"text":"anything subjective or emotional."},{"time":624674,"text":"We talk about the results."},{"time":626537,"text":"So there was no way to talk about it in conferences."},{"time":628606,"text":"That was unthinkable."},{"time":630530,"text":"And I saw scientists in other groups get stuck"},{"time":632606,"text":"without even having a word to describe"},{"time":634380,"text":"what they're seeing,"},{"time":635701,"text":"and their ways of thinking"},{"time":637056,"text":"narrowed down to very safe paths,"},{"time":638584,"text":"their science didn't reach its full potential,"},{"time":640244,"text":"and they were miserable."},{"time":641997,"text":"I thought, that's the way it is."},{"time":643936,"text":"I'll try to make my lab as creative as possible,"},{"time":645957,"text":"and if everybody else does the same,"},{"time":647637,"text":"science will eventually become"},{"time":649827,"text":"more and more better and better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":652041,"text":"That way of thinking got turned on its head"},{"time":654961,"text":"when by chance I went to hear Evelyn Fox Keller"},{"time":657300,"text":"give a talk about her experiences"},{"time":658658,"text":"as a woman in science."},{"time":660349,"text":"And she asked,"},{"time":662172,"text":"\"Why is it that we don't talk about the subjective"},{"time":664120,"text":"and emotional aspects of doing science?"},{"time":666306,"text":"It's not by chance. It's a matter of values.\""},{"time":670298,"text":"You see, science seeks knowledge"},{"time":672476,"text":"that's objective and rational."},{"time":674271,"text":"That's the beautiful thing about science."},{"time":676469,"text":"But we also have a cultural myth"},{"time":678425,"text":"that the doing of science,"},{"time":679679,"text":"what we do every day to get that knowledge,"},{"time":681979,"text":"is also only objective and rational,"},{"time":684419,"text":"like Mr. Spock."},{"time":686851,"text":"And when you label something"},{"time":688265,"text":"as objective and rational,"},{"time":690078,"text":"automatically, the other side,"},{"time":691720,"text":"the subjective and emotional,"},{"time":693177,"text":"become labeled as non-science"},{"time":695279,"text":"or anti-science or threatening to science,"},{"time":697250,"text":"and we just don't talk about it."},{"time":699061,"text":"And when I heard that,"},{"time":701015,"text":"that science has a culture,"},{"time":703182,"text":"everything clicked into place for me,"},{"time":704729,"text":"because if science has a culture,"},{"time":706393,"text":"culture can be changed,"},{"time":707649,"text":"and I can be a change agent"},{"time":709242,"text":"working to change the culture\nof science wherever I could."},{"time":711954,"text":"And so the very next lecture I gave in a conference,"},{"time":715023,"text":"I talked about my science,"},{"time":716635,"text":"and then I talked about the importance"},{"time":718147,"text":"of the subjective and emotional\naspects of doing science"},{"time":720329,"text":"and how we should talk about them,"},{"time":721449,"text":"and I looked at the audience,"},{"time":722683,"text":"and they were cold."},{"time":725043,"text":"They couldn't hear what I was saying"},{"time":728334,"text":"in the context of a 10 back-to-back"},{"time":729585,"text":"PowerPoint presentation conference."},{"time":731424,"text":"And I tried again and again,\nconference after conference,"},{"time":733906,"text":"but I wasn't getting through."},{"time":736279,"text":"I was in the cloud."}]},{"cues":[{"time":739185,"text":"And eventually I managed to get out the cloud"},{"time":742699,"text":"using improvisation and music."},{"time":745510,"text":"Since then, every conference I go to,"},{"time":748249,"text":"I give a science talk and a second, special talk"},{"time":751111,"text":"called \"Love and fear in the lab,\""},{"time":753104,"text":"and I start it off by doing a song"},{"time":755321,"text":"about scientists' greatest fear,"},{"time":757893,"text":"which is that we work hard,"},{"time":760805,"text":"we discover something new,"},{"time":763147,"text":"and somebody else publishes it before we do."},{"time":766504,"text":"We call it being scooped,"},{"time":769120,"text":"and being scooped feels horrible."},{"time":772334,"text":"It makes us afraid to talk to each other,"},{"time":774547,"text":"which is no fun,"},{"time":775380,"text":"because we came to science to share our ideas"},{"time":778140,"text":"and to learn from each other,"},{"time":779451,"text":"and so I do a blues song,"},{"time":785040,"text":"which — (Applause) —"},{"time":790544,"text":"called \"Scooped Again,\""},{"time":793767,"text":"and I ask the audience to be my backup singers,"},{"time":796425,"text":"and I tell them, \"Your text is 'Scoop, Scoop.'\""},{"time":800405,"text":"It sounds like this: \"Scoop, scoop!\""},{"time":803050,"text":"Sounds like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804013,"text":"♪ I've been scooped again ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":806232,"text":"♪ Scoop! Scoop! ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":807975,"text":"And then we go for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":809253,"text":"♪ I've been scooped again ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":811298,"text":"♪ Scoop! Scoop! ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":812584,"text":"♪ I've been scooped again ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":814479,"text":"♪ Scoop! Scoop! ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":815785,"text":"♪ I've been scooped again ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":817568,"text":"♪ Scoop! Scoop! ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":819207,"text":"♪ I've been scooped again ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":820875,"text":"♪ Scoop! Scoop! ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":822637,"text":"♪ Oh mama, can't you feel my pain ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":825912,"text":"♪ Heavens help me, I've been scooped again ♪"},{"time":830925,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":837735,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":838965,"text":"Thank you for your backup singing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":840464,"text":"So everybody starts laughing, starts breathing,"},{"time":842548,"text":"notices that there's other scientists around them"},{"time":844560,"text":"with shared issues,"},{"time":845867,"text":"and we start talking about the emotional"},{"time":847672,"text":"and subjective things that go on in research."},{"time":849522,"text":"It feels like a huge taboo has been lifted."},{"time":851706,"text":"Finally, we can talk about\nthis in a scientific conference."},{"time":854505,"text":"And scientists have gone on to form peer groups"},{"time":856691,"text":"where they meet regularly"},{"time":858301,"text":"and create a space to talk about the emotional"},{"time":859930,"text":"and subjective things that\nhappen as they're mentoring,"},{"time":862231,"text":"as they're going into the unknown,"},{"time":863594,"text":"and even started courses"},{"time":865164,"text":"about the process of doing science,"},{"time":866839,"text":"about going into the unknown together,"},{"time":868734,"text":"and many other things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":870150,"text":"So my vision is that,"},{"time":871484,"text":"just like every scientist knows the word \"atom,\""},{"time":874946,"text":"that matter is made out of atoms,"},{"time":876913,"text":"every scientist would know the words"},{"time":878397,"text":"like \"the cloud,\" saying \"Yes, and,\""},{"time":880741,"text":"and science will become much more creative,"},{"time":883820,"text":"make many, many more unexpected discoveries"},{"time":886824,"text":"for the benefit of us all,"},{"time":889360,"text":"and would also be much more playful."},{"time":891576,"text":"And what I might ask you to remember from this talk"},{"time":894166,"text":"is that next time you face"},{"time":896862,"text":"a problem you can't solve"},{"time":898588,"text":"in work or in life,"},{"time":901180,"text":"there's a word for what you're going to see:"},{"time":903056,"text":"the cloud."},{"time":904233,"text":"And you can go through the cloud"},{"time":905766,"text":"not alone but together"},{"time":907174,"text":"with someone who is your source of support"},{"time":909212,"text":"to say \"Yes, and\" to your ideas,"},{"time":911260,"text":"to help you say \"Yes, and\" to your own ideas,"},{"time":913577,"text":"to increase the chance that,"},{"time":915464,"text":"through the wisps of the cloud,"},{"time":917190,"text":"you'll find that moment of calmness"},{"time":918688,"text":"where you get your first glimpse"},{"time":920491,"text":"of your unexpected discovery,"},{"time":923741,"text":"your C."}]},{"cues":[{"time":926465,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":928785,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}